stitution.\r\nThe entire projects are developed as collaborative by the community and managed by the members inside. This collaboration is applied to the start up, developed by the community. Thus, all the projects and Start-Up developed inside W??Lab by the community became the community project or start-Up. \r\nW??Lab is an original project of The African architecture developed by Sénamé Koffi AGBODJINOU and inside the Smart African City program \" HubCité ! \"\r\n','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/UmTh8JngSsOmGLbZaFXB','0022893540826 / 0022891486366','woelabo@gmail.com | contact@woelabo.com','https://www.fablabs.io/woelab',976),(309,'BEC Fab Lab','The objective of the BEC Fab Lab is to help develop a community of inventors, entrepreneurs and enthusiasts who will benefit both from the facilities and the interaction it will provide, in the process helping to stimulate economic growth. Encouraging innovation is a significant part of the West Cumbria Economic Blueprint – a document which sets out a long-term vision for the region’s development based around low carbon energy.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/AL6PfE6DSWKAvbn0N66p','01900825080','becfablab@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/becfablab',174),(310,'FabLabFultonMO','FabLabFultonMo is equipped with two 3d printers ( expanding to four by summer 2014), an Epilog  laser, a Shopbot prs alpha 4896 cnc router, a vinyl cutter, a 3d scanner, table saw, planer, joiner, drill press and many smaller handtools. \r\nWe are adding a new metal band saw and a separate wood band saw as well as a cnc plasma cutter early next year,','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','5735908100','jhall@fulton58.org','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabfultonmo',178),(311,'FabLab Magdeburg','','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/Cc9hXhCfQ8ieIVhi2FwT','','fablab-inkubator@ovgu.de','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabmagdeburg',185),(312,'Industrial Studio ','\"Our study have two years of operating independently and this year we started to set up a workshop to accept bigger challenges\"','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','560976648528','lizama@industrialstudio.cl','https://www.fablabs.io/industrialstudio',191),(313,'L1A Makerspace','Die L1A Makerspace e.V. Werkstatt ist seit Juli 2015 geschlossen.\r\n\r\nWeiter geht es bei: http://www.Makerspace-Darmstadt.de\r\n','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/WSFKDCZOQYKnCv0LgaL1','','','https://www.fablabs.io/l1amakerspace',602),(315,'fablab Q8','creative center to lead community to better future','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/oP0SSkJQQ3CMr90eE6Py','+96599740064','fablabq8@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabq8',196),(316,'WeMake | Makerspace Fablab','WeMake is a makerspace where you can make things and connect with  people in Milan. \r\n\r\nUn makerspace dove creare cose e connetterti a una community, a Milano.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/iscmmo2zSMiuPjAK5NAY','+393298616599','hello@wemake.cc','https://www.fablabs.io/wemake',231),(317,'FABLAB Sardegna Ricerche  ','','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/fLZux6c4QLePtjrH1bEQ','+39 070 92432265','fablab@sardegnaricerche.it','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabsardegnaricerche',215),(318,'Fab Lab Floripa','We are studing our local community (makers, hackers, students and entrepreneurs) so we can build a strong Fab Lab based on people\'s needs. We want to combine digital and manual manufacturing to enhance innovation and create a collabotarive makerspace, given respect and responsability in a shared environment. \r\n\r\nWe are promoting workshops to disseminate the principles of Fab Lab network, democratizing the new digital fabrication technologies and bringing knowledge to everyone. We are also looking for companies and partners who want to support our Fab Lab so we can buy our first machines. \r\n\r\nFor more information, please visit: http://fablabfloripa.wordpress.com/ (in portuguese)','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/oAanToGQUur4esS7ZhjT','','fablabfloripa@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabfloripa',345),(319,'Fab Lab Recife','Como num primeiro encontro deixe que nos apresentemos: somos o Fab Lab Recife. Se você já ouviu falar de nós, fique mais um pouco e nos conheça um pouco mais; se ainda não ouviu, essa é uma ótima oportunidade pra isso. Seja bem vindo, o prazer é todo nosso. \r\n\r\nO Fab Lab Recife é para makers, curiosos e empreendedores de todas as áreas. Uma boa ideia pode vir de qualquer pessoa, ainda que sem conhecimento sobre fabricação digital. E como um de nossos propósitos é promover a formação e dar autonomia para que você crie suas próprias coisas, oferecemos, todos os meses, workshops básicos. Além disso, temos clubes, degustação e também um dia para uso livre (Open Day).\r\n\r\nCrianças e adolescentes têm um lugar especial no Fab Lab Recife. Queremos trazer à superfície a capacidade inventiva que todos temos na infância e que vai sendo reprimida com o passar dos anos. Queremos que eles soltem a criatividade e que os adultos retomem a sua. Criar é sempre um processo lúdico, ainda que para fins muito específicos. A economia criativa e a capacidade de inovar de maneira contínua são a chave para nossas questões sociais, econômicas e ambientais. E nós levamos isso muito a sério.\r\n\r\nAgora que já nos apresentamos, você já sabe quem somos e o que fazemos, queremos conhecer você, suas ideias e, claro, o que podemos fazer juntos. E podemos muito.\r\n\r\n******************\r\n\r\nAs in a first meeting let us introduce ourselves: we are the Fab Lab Recife. If you have already heard of us, stay awhile and get to know us better; if you haven’t, this is a great opportunity to do so. Welcome, it’s our pleasure.\r\n\r\nFab Lab Recife is a place for makers, curious and entrepreneurs from all fields. A good idea can come from anyone and they don’t necessarily have to know about digital manufacturing. That’s why one of our purposes is to promote training and empower people to create their own things, by offering every month basic workshops. We have also membership plans, tasting visits and a day for free use of the lab (Open Day).\r\n\r\nKids and teenagers have a special place at Fab Lab Recife. We want to bring to light the inventiveness that we all have in childhood and it’s suppressed over the years as we grow old. We want them to loosen their creativity and also that the adults recover their own. Creation is always a playful process, even when it’s intended for very specific purposes. The creative economy and the ability to innovate continuously are the key to our social, economic and environmental issues. And we take it very seriously.\r\n\r\nNow that we’ve introduced ourselves, you already know who we are and what we do. We also want to know you, your ideas and, of course, what we can do together. And we might.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/3200IhENS8GBO2PCuQIt','+55 81 3032.0222','redes@fablabrecife.com','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabrecife',808),(320,'ouagalab','ouagalab est un projet de laboratoire de fabrication numérique qui a pour but la création d\'un plateau d\'expressions. Il se veut de rassembler les passionnés de la création numérique afin de stimuler l’esprit de créativité et de partage de connaissances.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/LUQZAiYNRSO1qPxHjUqf','+22670766380/+22678927197','gildasguiella@yahoo.fr  gildasguiella@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/ouagalab',303),(321,'FabLab la Côte','Since the 07th of July we are installed in Nyon.\r\nABC Architecture puts us at disposal a place to start our activities.\r\nFor the moment it\'s just a small place but we can make some meetings and do some stuffs with the 3D printer and Lasercutter.\r\n\r\nWe\'ve installed also a small CNC mill, an oscilloscope,  a soldering station, few electronic components, some arduino kits and a computers.\r\n\r\nThis place is temporary because of ABC Architecures activities.\r\nWe continue our research for a bigger place to accomodate more people and more machines.\r\n\r\nWe hope to find a place as soon as 