ve research platform in design and artisan know-how that aims to develop projects with high territorial impact through the use of models of multidisciplinary and inter-generational co-creation. Built in local values, culture and lifestyle of Alentejo, the Buinho seeks to be a reference point of transdisciplinary R&D in Alentejo, bringing together creative projects that bridge technological factors to knowledge of the local craft traditions. \r\n\r\nOur goal is to develop and allow:\r\n- Innovative approaches in the field of education which connect artistic education with mathematics, engineering, science and technology;\r\n- Transfer of knowledge and research practices applied in rural areas;\r\n- Training of local populations and use of design methodologies services to promote youth empowerment;\r\n- A social and environmental structured approach to ensure the sustainability of projects;\r\n- A specialized offer prototyping solutions within an international network FabLabs and maker spaces.\r\n\r\n\r\nBuinho was born as a spin-off created by researchers at the University of Lisbon. Our motto is \"Buinho, time to play\"','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/rQY9X7ZdTJOXvXwhESh9','+351918283288','info@buinho.pt','https://www.fablabs.io/buinhofablab',839),(1094,'Edgewood Middle School Fab Lab','','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','','','https://www.fablabs.io/edgewoodmiddleschoolfablab',456),(1096,'fablab Ugent','','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','','kurt.vanhoutte@ugent.be','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabugent',474),(1097,'FabLab Senai-UEMS','','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','(67) 3902-2692','dcbraz@uems.br','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabsenaiuems',494),(1098,'Lab Maker Mocorongo','O LabMocorongo é um espaço maker livre, que conta com impressora 3D, equipamentos de eletrônica, Arduinos e vários componentes. Está a serviço de empreendimentos liderados por jovens que viabilizem a prototipação de soluções que unam a tecnologia e criatividade para problemas da cidade 