erience from every point of view;\r\n\r\nThe Lab, embodying a nevralgic center of creative connections, looks at the excellence of our territory , encourages  trainers even experiencing new professions aiming to give value to the craftsmanship and to the know-how exchange  looking ahead to a better future.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/AaO9GHCcTPGxAM7V52It','+3908231548645','kromlaboro@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/Kromlaboro',626),(1136,'Kamorking38','Woodworking FabLab. ??????? ?? ???????????????, 3D ??????????????, ????????????????, 3D ??????, ?????????????, ???????? 3D ??????????????.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/DLhYOgA7T8K9GVs8qSZU','','hackerspace@kamorking.ru','https://www.fablabs.io/kamorking',631),(1137,'FABLAB FREEFORM','FreeForm Solution Pte Ltd was established in 2003 and have been providing 3D technology solutions.\r\nTechnology such as 3D Scanning, 3D Engineering Machine through Design & 3D Printing.\r\nWe are a team of experienced professionals with engineering and design backgrounds.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/ZEEXW5m5RNKAS51CHjh6','+65 68344234','fablab@freeform.sg','https://www.fablabs.io/FreeForm',385),(1139,'Fablab Puiching (Macao)','Founded in April 2015, the Fablab Puiching (Macao) is operated by Macao Puiching Middle School. We hope we can create a platform for people to interact and share their ideas. We have various equipment such as 3D-printers and CNC milling machines, which can be capable for us to fabricate our creations and realize our ideas. Open for public on Saturday afternoon and Sunday morning. ','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/zXi3i9aRSgGIK5uiTutq','(853) 2852 9333','thomaslao@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/puichingmacao',868),(1140,'Maker Lab','Hello guys, we are \"Maker Lab\", a mini makerspace at Kaohsiung, Taiwan.\r\nWe have regular activities with local community \"Maker\'s Attic\" on every Thursday night.\r\nSeveral volunteers manage our lab together, coordinate workshop, arrange schedu