laying the foundation for a European-type higher school in Georgia, based on Georgian educational traditions. \r\nFab Lab offers to all entrepreneurs, students, professors and citizens full service of product prototyping and business consulting. ','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/qoOpsVkRxCwQ7BXCf7Mc','+995571010503','fab.lab@tsu.ge','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabtsu',291),(1230,'FAB LAB NOLA at Delgado Community College','Fab Lab NOLA at Delgado Community College Vision is to have New Orleanians change the world through science and math.\r\n\r\nFab Lab Nola mission is to inspire New Orleanians in becoming the next generation of innovators. Through hands-on learning, we cultivate a passion for math, science and digital fabrication.\r\n\r\nFab Lab NOLA is made possible through funding from Chevron as part of their overall commitment to STEM learning locally in New Olreans and throughout the US.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/R9HiOacaQUakhsg3ztjz','225.439.6612','sprove@dcc.edu','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabnola',595),(1231,'Fab Lab Akld','fab lab Auckland aims at opening in 2018, which a focus on sustainable development. The project will begin early 2017. Its specific objectives will be defined during that year, according to the needs identified in this area and the vision of the core team.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/3Hm5tuotRBy7ZHoZK2UR','02102855674','jbnatali@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabauckland',1000),(1236,'fablab\'ke','OÙ ?  /  WAAR ?\r\nÀ la Maison des Cultures et de la Cohésion Sociale de Molenbeek. En 2017 un FabLab mobile sera également \r\nproposé.\r\nIn het Huis van Culturen en Sociale Samenhang van Molenbeek krijgt het Fablab’ke een vaste werkplek en vanaf 2017 is er ook een mobiele unit beschikbaar voor scholen en partners.\r\n\r\nQUAND ?  /  WANNEER ?\r\nTu as 12 ans ou plus ? Alors rejoins-nous les mercredis (entre 14h et 16h). Le samedi de 10h30 à 13h30, le « Familylab » est ouvert pour toi et les membres de ta famille. Des stages seront également proposés en période scolaire et extrascolaire.\r\nVanaf 12 jaar ben je iedere woensdagnamiddag (van 14u tot 16u) welkom. Op zaterdagochtend kan je terecht met een ouder of familielid in het «Familylab », ongeacht je leeftijd (van 10u30 tot 13u30). Tijdens schoolvakanties zijn er stages in het FabLab’ke en buiten de vakanties zijn er schoolprojecten.\r\n\r\nÀ l’initiative de la Bourgmestre de la Molenbeek-Saint-Jean en charge de la Culture, Françoise \r\nSchepmans, de l’Échevine de la Cohésion sociale, Sarah Turine, et du Collège échevinal.\r\nOp initiatief van de Burgemeester van Sint-Jans-Molenbeek bevoedg voor Cultuur, Françoise \r\nSchepmans, van de Schepen van Sociale samenhang, Sarah Turine, en het Schepencollege.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/Bu0jqsNURFqN6m1CeClt','','info@fablabke.be','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabke',480),(1239,'Fab Lab Gwangju','The programs for the public that we offer includes\r\n- Weekly session: \r\n  teaching how to use digital fabrication tools including laser cutter, 3D printer, 3D scanner and CNC milling machine.\r\n- Monthly workshop: \r\n  focused to a specific that is related to open-source hardware and software such as arduino, open-source drone and various DIY projects.\r\n- Bi-monthly forum: \r\n  share and introduce emerging technology that has impact on our society by inviting professionals in the field.\r\n- Special session: \r\n  6-week-long program that allows public to prototype their idea that involves digital fabrication process. Each individuals are encouraged to make whatever they want and we provide professional assistance during the process.\r\n- Yearly hacker-thon: \r\n  we host hacker-thon mainly focused on \"automotive vehicles\" as we are supported by Hyundai motors. \r\n\r\nAnyone can join the programs that we offer and use the required tools at no charge due to the funding from Korean Government, Gwangju city administration and Hyundai Group. \r\nThe goal of this lab is to spread maker culture in this city by providing free access to the tools and also giving opportunity to make and share their own creation.\r\n\r\n*Tool list*\r\n1. 3D Printer: Open Creators - Almond 7ea/ FDM/ bedsize: 150*150*140mm\r\n2. 3D Printer: 3D systems - Projet660 1ea/ Full color SLS/ bedsize: 254*381*203mm\r\n3. 3D Printer: Uniontech - RS6000 1ea/ SLA / bedsize: 600*600*450mm\r\n4. 3D Scanner: LMI Technology - R1X 1ea\r\n5. Laser Cutter: Universial Laser - VLS3.50 2ea\r\n6. CNC: Manix - MM300S 1ea\r\n7. Thermo-hygrostat: Samwon Tech - Temi 300 1ea\r\n8. Oscilloscope: Tektronix - MDO4054B 3 1ea\r\n9. Function generator: Tektronix - AFG3021C 1ea\r\n10. Universial tester: Instron -10ST 1ea\r\n11. Electrochemical analyzer: Won A Tech - ZIBE1 1ea\r\n12. Particle size Analyzer: Microtrac- S3500 1ea\r\n13. Thermo-graphic camera: Juwon Tech- Avio G100EX 1ea\r\n14. Hand tools for Cutting, Polishing, Soldering and etc,. ','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/iHUKQpQ7RViv145hCTkA','+827042801012','openlabmaster@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabgwangju',1008),(1243,'SOCOM Fab Lab','Full-up Fab Lab plus a variety of other equipment. ','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','8138265149','michael.guinn@socom.mil','https://www.fablabs.io/socomfablab',961),(1244,'FabLab@TUHH','','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/JdihVV97T0qTANQBMgHe','','','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabtuhh',1007),(1246,'Rocket Fab Lab','This is the Fab Lab located in South Milwaukee High School in South Milwaukee, Wisconsin.  We are a suburban high school of 1200 students.  Go Rockets!','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/eygaiTCHRraVqja9WwGQ','414-766-5133','ewolbach@sdsm.k12.wi.us','https://www.fablabs.io/RocketFabLab',988),(1247,'erfindergarden Munich ','erfindergarden started as minecraft hacking workshop with the raspberrry pi for children aged 9 to 14  that we tought in fablabs all over Europe and at a regular Friday Pi club in Munich. Since August 2016 we are building up our own lab in the center of Munich with about 80m2. We are very open with two big shop windows and first want to get the neighbourhood community involved in making.  We are inspired by the ways children learn when they are on their own like painting with hands or building things with legos or minecraft blocks instead of being forced to remember facts and figures. We want to replicate this style of learning and give them the playground to create, explore and experiment with digital and also non digital fabrication tools. \r\n\r\nWe will have the complete list of fab tools before the end of 2016 like a big CNC, Lasercutter, VinylPlotter, Precision Milling and 3D Printers. At the moment we are starting with our 4 3D Printers, a Precision Desktop Mill, a 3D Scanner, Soldering equipment and hand tools. \r\n\r\nBig kids can use the lab every Wednesday evening. As part of the international fablab network we will be the first lab to offer the fabacademy course - the offical program to train fab lab staff called \"How to make (almost) anything\"  in the South of Germany starting in February 2017. If you are interested send us an mail to academy@erfindergarden.de.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/tHVWnkNrTmCttSOHuFq1','+4915124122746','play@erfindergarden.de','https://www.fablabs.io/erfindergarden',992),(1249,'Knox Labs','Knox Labs is a non-profit community-operated Makerspace located at 1 Public Sq.  Suite 2 Mount Vernon, OH in a 2,000 sq ft Office. The purpose of Knox Labs is provide the community with access to a space where people with common interests, in computers, machining, technology, woodworking, electronics and innovation can meet, socialize, collaborate, and build projects.\r\n\r\nOur mission is to provide our community with a place for the public to have access to machinery, and technology. Through community outreach we aim to stimulate economic development, and function as a center for peer learning and knowledge sharing in the form of workshops, presentations, and lectures and offer social activities for the public.\r\n\r\n','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/4uk7hucR5i6XGPE4hjaw','7402631120','info@knoxlabs.org','https://www.fablabs.io/knoxlabs',223),(1251,'Ota Fab','Our lab is owned by the 10 or more units of the 3D printer, and includes other 3D scanner also, laser cutter, a UV printer. In our lab, regularly 3D CAD and 3D printer - has held workshops and events.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/T8Kv2zr3TjSIRk4RwPzz','+81364287162','mail@smls.link','https://www.fablabs.io/otafab',620),(1252,'Ecolia Labs','Ecolia Labs a pour objectif de stimuler et accompagner l\'innovation technologique à travers la promotion de l\'entrepreneuriat des jeunes et des femmes au Cameroun, Suivant trois axes : \r\n\r\n- Accompagner les jeunes porteurs d\'idées et de projets innovants dans la création, la viabilisation et la pérennisation de leur startUp.\r\n\r\n- Combattre l\'exclusion sociale des jeunes et des femmes en les formant aux métiers du numérique.\r\n\r\n- Promouvoir les TIC dans l’éducation au Cameroun et en Afrique.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/9W3lfWnFQouesdnriTOH','+237 677 56 87 66 / 691 42 24 43','contact@ecolialabs.org','https://www.fablabs.io/ecolialabs',144),(1253,'FabLab Coimbra','Os nossos recursos e competências estão focados na investigação, e no apoio à realização de projectos, tanto individuais como empresariais. Colaboramos em termos correntes com diversas empresas e escolas em áreas como arquitectura, engenharia, tecnologias da saúde, artesanato, design, entre outros.\r\nA partilha de conhecimentos é aquilo que nos une como Makers, ferramenta principal na materialização de ideias inovadoras.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/ZZpDMx7fSqKEaWMR2Idg','239 497 730','fablab@novotecna.pt','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabcoimbra',757),(1254,'Fablabaro','Very well equipped fab lab with several 3D modeling and printing facilities, CNC milling, laser cutting, vinyl plotters and electronics prototyping lab.\r\nThe laboratory is inside a primary school and it is opened to public all days in the afternoon and evening.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/cIb9SIJQ1u8C2Km9qaAl','+393477526331','info@fablabscuola.it','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabaro',998),(1255,'Fablab Arras','Le fablab de la ville d\'Arras','https://i.imgur.com/iymHWkm.png','','perspectives@3d-nord.fr','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabarras',760),(1256,'Hope Lab','Our vision for is to transform it into FabLab Hope. From PBL (Project Based Learning) to Problem Based Learning, achieving solutions through digital fabrication, FabLab Hope will involve the entire community -- people of all ages from all cultural and ethnic backgrounds, regardless of nationality – using new, innovative educational methods, founded on a curriculum that focuses both on the collective and on the individual. The sharing of knowledge on a daily basis will engender good will and promise, when PF (Personal Fabrication) – where everyone can design and implement his/her own projects – can lead to\r\ncollective change.\r\nWe believe that the the current industrial revolution will lead to democratization in design and manufacturing,\r\nwhen the product is in its idea stage as well as in its implementation phase. Together we can achieve the\r\nnecessary equality to be makers of the future, using the FabLab infrastructure, development process, and,\r\nmost of all, the FabLab spirit, to achieve a global revolution.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/9Er9PDwQr26oz0pNlm6C','+972-54-666-2046','ohad@fablab-israel.org','https://www.fablabs.io/hopelab',1001),(1257,'FABLABSERGIPE','LABORATÓRIO DE TECNOLOGIAS DE ULTIMA GERAÇÃO COM O OBJETIVO DE  DESENVOLVER UMA CULTURA DE APRENDIZAGEM ATRAVÉS DA PRATICA COM A REALIZAÇÃO E OU CONSTRUÇÃO DE PROJETOS DOS MAIS DIFERENTES SEGUIMENTOS.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/8ORsjV4oQem5CF0XrUOA','+55 79 2105-3488 / +55 79 99891-4037','contato@fablabsergipe.com.br','https://www.fablabs.io/fablabsergipe',999),(1258,'BERIC','1. BERIC is  the public organization as a branch of Busan Metropolitan City Office of Education. \r\n2. The target of all our program is all the teachers and students in Busan area. \r\n3. We focus on providing the Creative Activities using the new tools and devices such as 3D printer, Laser cutter and Paper cutter etc\r\n4. Finacial issue : All the budget of our organization is from the government so all the programs are provided in free \r\n5. Facilities : 2 Labs \r\n6. Website : http://www.busanedu.net','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/ThOvBHHuQLCplH3GBYET','82-51-860-6114','happymanual@korea.kr','https://www.fablabs.io/beric',469),(1267,'Tacuru Fab Lab','Tacuru FabLab es una plataforma abierta de prototipado donde el intercambio de conocimientos es esencial.\r\nEl énfasis igual se pone en fomentar una dinámica multidisciplinaria e intergeneracional entre las nuevas empresas, diseñadores, arquitectos, ingenieros, aficionados, investigadores, estudiantes y así sucesivamente.\r\n\r\nTacuru FabLab is an open prototyping platform where knowledge sharing is essential.\r\nThe same emphasis is put on fostering a multidisciplinary and intergenerational dynamic between new companies, designers, architects, engineers, amateurs, researchers, students and so on.','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/e1KPYdP3Q0WEAsFvqduB','+54 3755 427978','tacurufablab@gmail.com','https://www.fablabs.io/tacurufablab',362),(1271,'Fablab Imola','\r\nWe set up a digital fabrication laboratory inside Technical School \"Alberghetti\" in Imola. We started in Feb. 28, 2015.\r\nThe lab is managed by external partner and we collaborate with schools to develop project and create connection with startup, freelance and company of our region.\r\nWe provide for our associated equipment such as 3D printers, Laser Cutter, 3D Scanners, Software for design, welders for electronic boards, Arduino boards','https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/wHaJzpbRXKwqNrvbSoF2','+393477187856','fablabimola@gmail.com','https://www.f